g the concomitant use of remdesivir with drugs that can reduce renal function.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/241039/', '', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Simeprevir, Amprenavir, Cabotegravir, Zanamivir, Lenacapavir, Telaprevir, Velpatasvir, Etravirine, Dolutegravir, More', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Maraviroc, Amprenavir, Simeprevir, Zanamivir, Cabotegravir, Lenacapavir, Telaprevir, Velpatasvir, Rilpivirine, More', 1767369485);
